\(\angle B=$angB ^\circ \)  find the other \(\angle A\) and the 
remaining sides \(a\) and \(b\). Give your answer to at least 3 decimal places.
$PAR
\{$al->print_q\}        
END_TEXT

$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;
